\newlabel{fig:comparison_training}{{13}{9}{Qualitative generations for two prompts under the same 8-step DDIM, CFG$=5.0$ setting. Top: ``Hello.'' Bottom: ``Thank you.'' The model changes coarse pose patterns across prompts, but both outputs remain noisy and low-detail}{figure.caption.21}{}}
